resources.string: Accessibility service is used to simulate touch screen events for remote control of the device.
This app uses accessibility service to simulate user interface events. The accessibility permissions screen will now open. Please grant accessibility permissions to the "Headwind Remote" app.

Oh, no! Looks like Accessibility services required by Headwind Remote are not available on your device! Please contact the developers at https://headwind-remote.com and report which is your device model. We hope it will be supported in the future and your help is appreciated!
